title: Features & Benefits of a Thule Trail Carrier Basket
description: This premium carrier basket features integrated T-tracks for the seamless addition of your other Thule accessories.

asset.title: Carrier basket - Thule Trail
asset.description:
Are you looking for a premium carrier basket for the roof of your car? Watch this video and learn how to install Thule Trail, and how to combine it with Thule carriers and bags.

Thule Trail
The premium carrier basket with integrated functions.

- Exclusively designed in silver aluminium with black contrast elements.
- Integrated side consoles for greater security.
- Integrated T-tracks for seamlessly adding other Thule products. Extends basket use.
- Non-slip rubber padding for loading long objects.
- Lockable to load carrier.
- Points of attachment adjustable to the load carrier in length.

Learn more at www.thule.com
asset.author: ThuleBringYourLife
